@Node "Overview" "ADGLookUp | Overview"

	ADGLookUp  is  a rexx program, to be used with CygnusEd.  I made this program,
because  I  had all my AutoDocs translated into AmigaGuide format by using AD2AG
(released  by  Commodore  together with AmigaGuide), and I wanted a quick way of
accessing  these files.  This is done by scanning for the keyword wanted, in the
xreference  file  created  by AD2AG (or AD2HT), and then calling AmigaGuide with
the  apropiate  file  and  node.   It  also  searches  for  structures  and even
includefiles!
@EndNode

